       <p><b><a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/c-a-hellas-certified-public-accountants/">C & A Hellas</a></b> Certified Public Accountants and Business Consultants was established in 2016. Our Partners are distinguished professionals with a significant experience in Audit in Greece as well as abroad.</p>
       <p>Our company’s founder is <b><a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/antonis-papadopoulos-797195134">Antonis Papadopoulos</a></b>, a certified member of the Greek Association of Certified Public Accountants and also a member of the Association of International Accountants of the United Kingdom. His experience starts from the 70’s when he started working in the United Kingdom, before moving to Cyprus and then to Greece. He has been associated with two of the BIG 4 audit firms, but has also worked with smaller audit firms.</p>
       <p>Managing Director and co-founder of our company is <b><a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/christina-papadopoulou-75083b3b">Christina Papadopoulou</a></b>. Her experience as an employee of one of the BIG 4 audit firms for more than 10 years, in addition to her recent experience working in Luxembourg, has given her the opportunity to work on audits of complex organization and group of companies in a variety of sectors, such as Tourism, Service Providers, Manufacturing and Real Estate. She is a certified member of the Greek Association of Certified Public Accountants and has excellent knowledge of the Greek Accounting Standards as well as International Financial Reporting Standards. </p>
       <p>Our principal strength is the personal attention that is given to our clients by both the partners and staff. The members of C & A Hellas are certified professionals with expertise in audit services and profound understanding of the challenges that organisations face in today’s economic environment. In addition, our staff is technology literate, attend all required seminars related to our profession and most speak more than one foreign language. </p>
       <p>Our main objective is for our staff to be able to identify issues and find appropriate solutions with flexibility in a timely manner and using critical judgement. In addition, we work with them to cultivate their creativity, as well as their ability to provide practical solutions.</p>
       <p>Despite our recent incorporation, our firm has a significant number of clients due to the quality of our services, as well as the skills, experience and solvency of its founders. Our clientele covers a wide range of commercial activity such as shipping and shipmanagement, offshore offices, service providers, manufacturing and industrial concerns.</p>
       <p>Partners and staff make every effort to provide high quality services to business enterprises in Greece and to business abroad which are interested in investing in Greece. Our international background and experience give us the advantage of understanding foreign investors and there concerns and the ability to provide them with the necessary information.</p>      
